data.description: Renovated and move in ready! This 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home has been updated and is ready for new owners! Updates include a new roof in 2023, fresh paint and brand new LVP flooring throughout the living space! This home offers a spacious living room that opens to the dining area. The kitchen is beautiful with custom cabinets, granite counters and stainless steel appliances. The garage has been converted and could be a bonus area or bedroom. Come picture yourself in the backyard with family and friends!
